---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
const challenges = [
    {
        title: "Feedback Seeker Challenge",
        text: "Ask 5 people for honest feedback on an idea/product to embrace constructive criticism.",
        icon: "mdi:message-processing-outline",
    },
    {
        title: "Stranger High-Five Challenge",
        text: "Ask 10 strangers for a high-five or fist bump to reduce social anxiety and build confidence.",
        icon: "mdi:eye-outline",
    },
    {
        title: "Upsell Me Challenge",
        text: "Say 'no' to first offers in 3 stores to observe sales tactics and handle objections.",
        icon: "mdi:hand-coin-outline",
    },
];
---

<section class="w-full bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-gray-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto py-20 px-5 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
            <div class="w-full flex justify-center mb-6">
                <div
                    class="border border-primary text-primary text-sm rounded-full px-2 font-medium"
                >
                    Build Resilience
                </div>
            </div>
            {/* Headline - Antimetal's clean style */}
            <h2
                class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-base-content mb-6 tracking-tight"
            >
                Real World Challenges
            </h2>

            {/* Body Text - Improved readability */}
            <p
                class="text-lg text-base-content/80 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 text-justify"
            >
                Entrepreneurial resilience is the non-negotiable survival skill
                for business. Success hinges on your mental fortitudeâ€”the
                ability to absorb the inevitable rejection and failure, learn,
                and persistently move forward. Overcome mental blocks through
                these real-world challenges designed to rewire your response to
                fear and distraction, forging the resilience required for
                success.
            </p>
        </div>

        {/* Three Core Challenges */}
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
            {
                challenges.map((challenge) => {
                    return (
                        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-base-200 hover:shadow-md transition-all relative">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                                <Icon
                                    name={challenge.icon}
                                    class="text-xl text-primary"
                                />
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">
                                {challenge.title}
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-base-content/80">{challenge.text}</p>
                        </div>
                    );
                })
            }
        </div>
        <div class="w-full flex justify-end">
            <a
                href="/challenges"
                class="inline-flex items-center btn btn-primary px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium"
            >
                Explore Free Challenges
                <Icon name="mdi:chevron-right" class="text-2xl text-white" />
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
